text: A video game that is an absolute masterpiece is Super Mario Galaxy.  The gameplay utilizes the Wiimote in the best way possible and I feel getting each star involves a quality task.  Super Mario Galaxy shows that the Wii can have excellent graphics if you just put a lot of effort into them.  Koji Kondo continues to amaze people with his music and the orchestra just fits perfectly with a space-themed game.  This game shows that Shigeru Miyamoto can still create excellent games.
